data.name: Label3.Text
data.value: To add items to the play list: 1. Add song lyrics from the database using the Search pane below. 2. Drag and drop files from anywhere on the drive. You can display PowerPoint, Word, PDF or most media types. To Edit the Play List: '+' moves selected line down; '-' moves it up, 'DEL' deletes it Double click a line in the list to play just that song

data.name: ChkPause.ToolTip
data.value: All other files are under the control of the operator page by page, but videos and other media files start automatically then close on completion and move to the next. Pause provides some operator control
